# File Header Author Rule

- Never use AI/model names in `Created by` lines (for example: OpenAI, Codex, ChatGPT, Claude).
- Use the human author name `Grant Davis` for new file headers in this repository.
- Match the existing project header format (including copyright line and date format).
- If author context is missing, ask for the author instead of inventing one.

## Examples

```swift
//  Created by Grant Davis on 4/1/26.
//  Copyright © 2026 Cloudnine Weather. All rights reserved.
```

```swift
//  Created by OpenAI Codex on 4/1/26. // forbidden
```
